column1: Daily Weather Observations for Frankston, Victoria for March 2016
Prepared at 13:03 GMT on Thursday 14 April 2016   IDCJDW3028.201603
Most observations taken from Frankston, but rainfall taken from Mornington and pressure taken from Moorabbin Airport.
Mornington does not normally report on days when there was no rain.
Temperature, humidity and wind observations are from Frankston AWS {station 086371}
Pressure observations are from Moorabbin Airport {station 086077}
